--Read Me file for VR Game--

1. Once you've downloaded the file simply enter the directory of the download in the URL bar  

2. Click in Menu.unity to launch the game in unity (Note: have unity 2017 build to play)

3. Once the game is in the editor click the play button at the top of the screen

4. Give 5 seconds for the game to launch

5. Simply play the game for 1 minute.

6. Now that the minute is up simply stop the application by pressing the stop button on the top of the editor.


Assets used for music

main menu music and main game music:  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qlcSVP-BAWA

game over sound effect: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0HQzxgUbIbg
